\v 13 \x - \xo 2.13 \xt Tait 3.1\x*Gioęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su e koęž‰loęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, gamani kalu koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰waęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, ini towoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Gamani misaęž‰ kalu alan e waęž‰laęž‰b dofoęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ to eloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi.
\v 14 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gamani misaęž‰ kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gamaniloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ daęž‰fe alifeloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ ililoęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Kalu i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰walilaki falasilaęž‰meleaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale man nafaloęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰meleaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifaęž‰.
