\v 16 Gioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰kiloęž‰ sili alifaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale koęž‰loęž‰lab koęž‰sega, â€śNe sili alifaęž‰ gaęž‰li soęž‰boęž‰loęž‰bâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰asulakiyoęž‰, mogagoęž‰ aęž‰dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰ba. Gioęž‰ gaęž‰li sili alifaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale dowakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaęž‰bi.
