\v 18 \x - \xo 2.18 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.5\x*Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Gioęž‰ geloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab kalu aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, eloęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi. Boęž‰foęž‰lab kalu abeyoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰sa dowakiloęž‰, nafale dimidab aęž‰noęž‰lekoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰lba. Boęž‰foęž‰lab kalu abeyoęž‰ gioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰likiloęž‰ mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab i aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰lubi.
\v 19 Giyoęž‰ man halayoęž‰ moęž‰dimidoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu giloęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ nagaloęž‰woęž‰ gemoęž‰ madali dimialega, gi asuloęž‰woęž‰ Godemoęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰taki, nagaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega Gode eyoęž‰ man dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, gioęž‰ sagale alifaęž‰ib.
\v 20 \x - \xo 2.20 \xt 1Bid 3.14,17\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ giyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidalega, geloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ ge oęž‰li yamelaęž‰maęž‰ib. Eyoęž‰ ge saęž‰ndalikiyoęž‰ ge haęž‰sa dowaki, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lalega, â€śNe hidaęž‰yoęž‰ we haęž‰sa elena dioęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰ ne kalu nafale,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰ndoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰na iliki diab. Koęž‰sega giyoęž‰ man nafale dimidoęž‰ amioęž‰, ge nagaloęž‰woęž‰ madali diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ ge haęž‰sa dofoęž‰liki hidaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lalega, Gode eyoęž‰ giloęž‰ man nafa dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ sagale alifaęž‰ib.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2.21 \xt Madi 16.24, Yoęž‰n 13.15\x*Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ man nafa aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki aęž‰na hoęž‰idoęž‰. Moęž‰woęž‰ Keliso e gi asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰, nagaloęž‰woęž‰ e diaęž‰i ane. Gioęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leau kudu menaęž‰kiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ man we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na widoęž‰.
